			<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and inflicts burn.<br>If this skill is used during Eden mode, a variant<br>called Eden Code 05: Gevurah will be used instead.<br>Eden Code 05: Gevurah deals damage to<br>enemies directly ahead and inflicts scorchrend.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 213 × 4 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,476<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 5,571<br>Special Effects:<br>・Burn<br>　　Lasts 12 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 3.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 97<br><br><color=#00008B>Eden Mode:</color><br>Damage: 126 × 6 hits<br>Damage: 76 × 2 hits<br>Damage: 100 × 4 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,476<br>Special Effects:<br>・Scorchrend<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41.6<br></div></dd><dt
